narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Provide Care, Inc. is a Social Worker provider based in North Branch, MN. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $39.2M in Medicaid payments across 176K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $39.2M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
